    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Style of Chinese script joining elements of running and the standard scripts. It is less cursive than the typical running script, and thus more easily legible.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
          <Note_Contributor>
